      "actionDate": "2025-03-21",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>NICS Data Reporting Act</strong></p><p>This bill requires the Department of Justice to report annually on the demographic data of persons who are determined to be ineligible to purchase a firearm based on a background check performed by the National Instant Criminal Background Check System.</p>",
